      "Russia had pumped over seventeen billion dollars in economic support into Venezuela alone... loans, weapons purchases, oil investments. They had a 2025 Strategic Partnership Treaty with Maduro extending oil cooperation to 2041. They sold Maduro Su-30 fighters, S-300 air defense systems, Buk-M2E missiles. In the summer of 2024, they sailed warships into the Caribbean and docked in Havana... twice... as retaliation for Biden letting Ukraine use long-range munitions. They operated a global navigation satellite ground station in Nicaragua that American intelligence strongly suspected was being used for signals intelligence. Cuba was providing Russia with foreign fighters for the Ukraine war. Think about that. Cuban soldiers fighting in Ukraine against our allies, recruited through a regime ninety miles from Florida.",
